[154316.123435] BUG: unable to handle kernel NULL pointer dereference at 000000f4
[154316.123515] IP: scsi_block_requests+0xa/0x30

This is because aac_shutdown() does

        struct Scsi_Host *shost = pci_get_drvdata(dev);
